## ============================================================
## .gitignore cho dự án ASP.NET Core / Visual Studio
## ============================================================

# ── Build output ──────────────────────────────────────────────
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Ll]og/
[Ll]ogs/
out/
publish/

# ── Visual Studio ─────────────────────────────────────────────
.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.userprefs
*.pidb
*.vcxproj.filters

# ── NuGet ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
packages/
!**/packages/build/
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
artifacts/

# ── Rider / JetBrains ─────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
*.sln.iml

# ── VS Code ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json

# ── .NET / C# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.dll
*.exe
*.pdb
*.mdb
*.opencover.xml
*.coverage
*.coveragexml
TestResult.xml
[Tt]est[Rr]esult*/

# ── ASP.NET Core secrets / config nhạy cảm ────────────────────
appsettings.Development.json
appsettings.Local.json
secrets.json
*.pfx
*.p12

# ── Entity Framework / Migrations tạm ────────────────────────
# (Bỏ comment dòng dưới nếu không muốn commit migrations)
# Migrations/

# ── OS files ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Windows
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/

# macOS
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride

# ── Môi trường & biến nhạy cảm ────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# ── Publish profiles ──────────────────────────────────────────
**/Properties/PublishProfiles/
